Text:
COOL: @netflix has created an interactive site to showcase all of the past &amp; future productions shot in our beautiful state.

@netflix came for the beautiful scenery &amp; stayed for all of the wonderful opportunities we have to offer businesses. Check it out!
https://t.co/zMBrU6zZM5

ABQ is turning up the heat in the kitchen!

@Streetfood_NM has created something really special here in NM with the $2M I helped secure—an opportunity for folks to elevate their culinary skills into a sustainable small business.

Really fun seeing what these chefs are cooking up. https://t.co/ka032kLSgB

Partnerships between different municipalities when disaster strikes is essential.

@RMACCinfo &amp; @LosAlamosNatLab and I are working together to develop better fire suppression tactics &amp; burned area recovery efforts for New Mexicans.

Always getting better, together. https://t.co/5hkDvkvAf3
